==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Saree
<hw>Sa"ree</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind. <?/.]</ety>
<def>The principal garment of a Hindoo woman. It consists of a long
piece of cloth, which is wrapped round the middle of the body, a portion
being arranged to hang down in front, and the remainder passed across
the bosom over the left shoulder.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sargasso</ent>⟦br⟧
